{"tid":1308572,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"依家連網上文宣都少左","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T04:39:45.000Z","uid":261349,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cb982d1633ba3122ae353f70ff8df45aa3cd4fe9","tid":1308572,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"注意到「幫港出聲」d真藍絲留言又出哂來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網上宣傳遊行既人又少左好多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人轉移哂焦點，成日掛住黑警。<br />\n五大訴求呢？信用系統？監控燈柱？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個係危險既訊號來，我地好似返緊2014年</span><br />\n搞連儂牆唔係唔得，但要確保有足夠精力做其他行動。唔好因小失大。"},{"pid":"f3f9f59e32cc8ef38862c31db2091fb9c925688b","tid":1308572,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:28:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ecaca8ae4dd2eed92f7bc7f6ce2d78b0c5d1ed7","tid":1308572,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:31:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17a87cbd057f44e3d06f6a6149cdfc5629834982","tid":1308572,"uid":107216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:31:47.000Z","msg":"推 集中啲"},{"pid":"805b6683ed9fbb8e9f8c61971fc508a9741e9873","tid":1308572,"uid":270824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再不停嗌香港人加油，集中翻七大訴求既口號！<br />\n外國媒體起碼可以報導我地要既訴求！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n七大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n巴絲幫幫手推翻遊行POST上頂🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n一、撤銷反送中抗爭者控罪 <br />\n二、成立獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權 <br />\n三、實行真雙普選 <br />\n四、撤回引渡條例修訂草案<br />\n五、撤回6.12暴動定義<br />\n六、要求永不實行「社會信用評分系統」<br />\n七、徹回「多功能監控系統」"},{"pid":"d1596821b60d609637345f6dea1d66422f514b10","tid":1308572,"uid":206375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"af57d7b1c15d389404e378641694eef3d2cc047a","tid":1308572,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:37:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">立即停手，我而家嚴重警告你，唔好再襲擊<br />\n<br />\n我而家係制止你再打人，請立即停手<br />\n<br />\n我而家係公民拘捕你，因為你對我朋友施以實質傷害的襲擊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n然後幾個一齊撲上去<br />\n各位識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd8a933a69f27b3aca01c60ad1ff4071e3de3fd","tid":1308572,"uid":117892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:37:59.000Z","msg":"唔好俾啲鬼帶走個風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比起任何事 我只求每個義士平安歸隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n釋放所有被捕示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推到有更多被捕示威者嘅消息為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCJRxtX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCJRxtX.png&h=c5c66862&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qiao72i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQiao72i.png&h=2ed6ce87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b902e3efa4020590d138c22a2bb634387885ea1","tid":1308572,"uid":261349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我覺得大家要攞到共識: 第一，訴求愈來愈多，你要求十鳩幾樣野既時候，唔會有人記得。所以邊樣重要d我地要學識取捨。第二，行動要用咩方式，係和理非定勇武，係野餐定遊行，係攻係守，唔該講定。唔好再講各有各做，依家散到咁，要各做前首先要講低比大家知，d物資輿論先backup到。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲有，唔想重蹈2014年既覆轍，唔該唔好守連儂牆，唔好哂心力係其他地方。</span>"},{"pid":"21c74e2ef96d57f48211eeb1b403a030b2fcfb55","tid":1308572,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"218a5deede8ccc40e67b78f5bc5fd57ead3d1081","tid":1308572,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:49:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">覺得文宣小左既人 即刻係fb ig宣傳上水沙田</span></span>"},{"pid":"da6ba2517ff54a049e76c5d517885e29b212d13e","tid":1308572,"uid":89767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:43:49.000Z","msg":"大家喺ig幾個鐘post一個story，其實已經做到宣傳效果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8Rr6aG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8Rr6aG.png&h=19d7424e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cyn3oXn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCyn3oXn.png&h=74768491&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6imU33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6imU33.png&h=127b4ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLO2EvJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg